00:19:42.005 --> 00:19:44.665
But for now, in the short run,
there's no entry and exit.

00:19:44.665 --> 00:19:47.165
So whatever number of firms I
tell you, that's what's there.

00:19:47.165 --> 00:19:48.970
It's just given.

00:19:48.970 --> 00:19:50.470
So let's say n equals 6.

00:19:50.470 --> 00:19:52.767
Let's say there's six firms.

00:19:52.767 --> 00:19:54.850
And I'll come in a minute
