00:20:28.860 --> 00:20:30.780
They know there's six firms.

00:20:30.780 --> 00:20:31.530
So they're done.

00:20:31.530 --> 00:20:32.613
I'm going to come to this.

00:20:32.613 --> 00:20:34.200
You're talking about
the long run, OK?

00:20:34.200 --> 00:20:35.260
Other questions?

00:20:35.260 --> 00:20:36.510
Yeah-- OK.

00:20:36.510 --> 00:20:39.270
So that gives you
your market supply.

00:20:39.270 --> 00:20:44.220
Finally, we go back to lecture
one and the first recitation

00:20:44.220 --> 00:20:46.560
where you solved
