00:20:46.560 --> 00:20:47.668
We have a demand curve.

00:20:47.668 --> 00:20:48.960
I'm just going to make this up.

00:20:48.960 --> 00:20:53.790
Let's say the demand curve
is Q equals 40 minus p.

00:20:53.790 --> 00:20:55.867
I just made that up
