will buy from you.

00:35:43.890 --> 00:35:46.150
You never want to
set a price below $10

00:35:46.150 --> 00:35:47.610
because you'll lose money.

00:35:47.610 --> 00:35:51.700
Therefore, supply is perfectly
elastic at a price of $10.

